 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of information that describes the two dimensional shape of a component and that describes the two dimensional location of a component where the product context is a physical design view.
	   The shape of the component is provided only for the cases where the shape of the component is not available as a property of the
	   definition of the component.
   </p>
 </purpose>

